<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New User Notification</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #6366F1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      height: 100px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .section-title {
      background-color: #6366F1;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .order-status {
      background-color: #e7f7e7;
      color: #2e8b57;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .info-text {
      width: 60%;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .product {
      display: flex;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding: 15px 0;
    }
    .product-image {
      width: 80px;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }
    .product-image img {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .product-details {
      flex-grow: 1;
      display: block;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .product-name {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .product-price {
      color: #6366F1;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .product-quantity {
      color: #666;
    }
    .product-total {
      margin-left: auto;
      font-weight: bold;
      align-self: center;
      color: #6366F1;
    }
    .totals {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .total-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .grand-total {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #6366F1;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding-top: 10px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .actions {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6366F1;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white;
      background-color: #6366F1;
      margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .returning-customer {
      background-color: #10B981;
    }
    .new-customer {
      background-color: #F59E0B;
    }
    .bold {
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .user-history {
      background-color: #eef2ff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duzlv0fex/image/upload/v1744295709/urhndchpkmqiufym8mbv.png" alt="MinifigsMania">
      <h1>Welcome to MinifigsMania!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="order-status">
      You have successfully registered!
    </div>

    <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>Welcome to MinifigsMania! Please take the time to go through this email to complete your profile and get the most out of being a member.</p>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Next Steps</div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Verify Account</div>
        <div class="info-text">click here</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Perks of being a registered user</div>
    <div class="info-row">
      <div class="info-label">Wishlist</div>
      <div class="info-text">Add products to your wishlist!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
      <div class="info-label">Promotions</div>
      <div class="info-text">Access to new promotions and member only promotions!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
    <div class="info-label">Notifications</div>
    <div class="info-text">Opt in to recieve email notifications for new releases!</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
  <div class="info-label">Tracking</div>
  <div class="info-text">Easily track your orders!</div>
</div>
  </div>

  <p>If you have any questions, you can contact us <a href='http://localhost:5173/contact'>here</a>.</p>
  <p>If you want to opt out recieving notifications, please log in and change your settings.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated notification from your MinifigsMania store.</p>
      <p>Â© <%= Date.today.year %> MinifigsMania. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>